---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Resync Technology" description="About Resync Technology and its founder, Sergio Reyes — engineering-led execution, automation-first systems, and clean architecture.">
  <section class="bg-paper text-ink">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">

      <!-- Eyebrow -->
      <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm text-slateink shadow-soft">
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-resync-600"></span>
        About Resync Technology
      </p>

      <!-- Main Title -->
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-6xl">
        Built to solve real problems — with speed and clean execution.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slateink/80 max-w-2xl">
        Resync Technology is an engineering-led software studio. We design and build modern systems, automate operations, and ship reliable products with clean architecture. Small team energy. High-quality output. Fast shipping.
      </p>

      <!-- Values -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Engineering-led</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slateink/75">Real software built on strong foundations. No fluff. No shortcuts.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Automation-first</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slateink/75">Reduce manual work. Build leverage. Create repeatable workflows.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Reliable delivery</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slateink/75">Clear scope, transparent communication, and predictable timelines.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Founder Section -->
<div class="mt-16 rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white p-10 shadow-soft">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 md:flex-row md:items-start">
    <!-- Photo -->
    <div class="shrink-0">
      <img
        src="/SergioReyes.jpeg"
        alt="Sergio Reyes"
        class="h-28 w-28 rounded-full object-cover ring-4 ring-resync-100 shadow-soft"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Text -->
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Founder</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-resync-700">
        Sergio Reyes — Founder & CEO
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-slateink/80 leading-relaxed">
        I started programming in highschool, building websites, small games, and tools for fun. Over the years, that grew into a passion for software engineering, iOS development, and designing systems that actually help people work better. I’ve built full-stack applications, API integrations, internal tools, and automation pipelines — always focused on speed, reliability, and clean architecture.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-slateink/80 leading-relaxed">
        I launched Resync Technology to help small businesses, contractors, and growing teams upgrade their software without needing a huge engineering department. My goal is simple: build tools that feel fast, look clean, and make your daily workflow easier.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-slateink/80 leading-relaxed">
        Whether it's an iOS app, modern web app, automation system, or internal tool — I believe great software should be simple, dependable, and designed around real people.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


      <!-- Featured Project -->
      <div class="mt-16 rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white p-10 shadow-soft">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Featured Project</h2>

        <h3 class="mt-3 text-xl font-semibold">Invoice Americano</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slateink/80 leading-relaxed">
          An iOS invoicing app built for contractors, small business owners, and people who need professional invoices without expensive tools. Create invoices fast, send professional PDFs, keep track of client history, and connect payments seamlessly.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-black/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slateink">iOS</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-black/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slateink">Payments</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-black/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slateink">PDF Generation</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-black/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slateink">Automation</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-16 rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white p-10 shadow-soft">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Work with us</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-slateink/80 leading-relaxed">
          If you want a fast, reliable build with clean architecture — tell us what you’re trying to accomplish. I’ll help you scope it, plan it, and ship it efficiently.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/#contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl2 bg-resync-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-soft hover:bg-resync-700">
            Start a Project
          </a>
          <a href="/#work" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl2 border border-black/10 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slateink hover:bg-black/5">
            View Work
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
